ents by a gauge\ntheory observer and depend upon the mass scale --- once again, as expected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 May 2014 20:16:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Jun 2014 02:57:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
